---
const SITE_NAME = "The-Circle";
const DISCORD_INVITE = "https://discord.gg/9rPcHQZ7SH";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Discord Rules • {SITE_NAME}</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/svg+xml">
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="The-Circle Discord rules and moderation policy."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <header class="top">
        <div class="container nav">
          <a class="brand" href="/">
            <img
              src="/favicon.png"
              alt=""
              class="logo"
            />
            <span>{SITE_NAME}</span>
          </a>

          <nav class="links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/discord">Discord</a>
            <a href="/league">League</a>
            <a href="/Music">Music</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>

          </nav>


        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="container">
        <section class="hero">
          <div class="welcome">
            <h1>Discord Rules</h1>

            <p class="sub">
              To make sure everyone has a great time, please take a moment to read our community guidelines.
              Breaking these rules may result in a warning, mute, kick, or ban.
            </p>

            <div class="cta">
              <a class="btn primary" href={DISCORD_INVITE} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Discord</a>
              <a class="btn ghost" href="/discord">Back to Discord</a>
            </div>

            <p class="fine">
              This server is built to be chill. If something starts turning into drama, step back.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>Community guidelines</h2>

          <div class="stack">
            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>Be respectful</h3>
              <p>Treat everyone with kindness. No harassment, hate speech, or personal attacks.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>Keep it friendly</h3>
              <p>
                Avoid controversial topics like politics or religion, or anything that sparks arguments.
                This is a place to relax and have fun — keep those conversations elsewhere.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>No drama or arguments</h3>
              <p>
                If a conversation starts getting heated, step back.
                Don’t argue or try to “win” debates.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>Appropriate content only</h3>
              <p>
                No NSFW or illegal content, and no hateful or deliberately offensive language.
                Keep things comfortable for everyone.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>Respect privacy</h3>
              <p>Do not share personal information — yours or anyone else’s.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>Follow channel topics</h3>
              <p>Post in the correct channels. Off-topic content belongs in designated areas.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>No spamming or self-promotion</h3>
              <p>Avoid spam, excessive links, or unsolicited advertising.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>Listen to staff</h3>
              <p>
                Staff decisions are final. If you have concerns, contact them respectfully.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="ruleBlock">
              <h3>Have fun</h3>
              <p>Be positive, chill, and enjoy your time here.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="fine">
            If you have any questions, feel free to ask a moderator — we’re here to help.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>Punishments</h2>

          <p class="note">
            Moderation exists to keep the server enjoyable for everyone, not to punish people unnecessarily.
            Most issues start with a warning.
          </p>

          <div class="ruleBlock">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Every rule-breaking message:</strong> deleted + warning.</li>
              <li><strong>3 warnings in 30 minutes:</strong> 2 hour temporary mute.</li>
              <li><strong>5 warnings in 1 day:</strong> 30 day temporary ban.</li>
              <li><strong>7 warnings in 7 days:</strong> permanent ban.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="note">
              Staff may issue warnings for behavior not explicitly listed if it goes against the
              community’s spirit or safety.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container foot">
          <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {SITE_NAME}</span>
          <span class="muted">Discord rules</span>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <style is:global>
      html, body { height: 100%; }

      body{
        margin:0;
        min-height:100vh;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);

        background-image:
          radial-gradient(900px 500px at 15% 10%, rgba(9,255,3,0.14), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(800px 450px at 85% 15%, rgba(120,170,255,0.18), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(700px 450px at 55% 95%, rgba(255,170,120,0.10), transparent 55%),
          linear-gradient(#070a0f, #070a0f);

        background-repeat:no-repeat;
        background-size:100% 100%;
        background-attachment:fixed;
      }

      a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
      .container{ max-width: 1020px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 18px; }

      .page{ min-height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
      main{ flex:1; }

      .top{
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        background: rgba(7,10,15,0.55);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      }

      .nav{
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:space-between;
        padding:14px 18px;
        gap:14px;
      }

      .brand{
        display:flex;
        gap:10px;
        align-items:center;
        font-weight:800;
        letter-spacing:-0.02em;
        white-space:nowrap;
      }

      .logo{
        width:30px;
        height:30px;
        display:block;
      }

      .links{ display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:center; }
      .links a{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); font-size:14px; }
      .links a:hover{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); }

      .pill{
        padding:10px 12px;
        border-radius:999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(9,255,3,0.24);
        background: rgba(9,255,3,0.10);
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      }

      .mobileJoin{ display:none; }

      .hero{ padding: 34px 0 10px; }

      .welcome{
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
        padding: 22px;
      }

      h1{ margin:0 0 10px; font-size: 40px; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
      h2{ margin:0 0 10px; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
      h3{ margin:0 0 6px; font-size: 16px; }

      .sub{
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.74);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 92ch;
      }

      .note{
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.70);
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 92ch;
      }

      .fine{
        margin-top: 12px;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .cta{
        display:flex;
        gap:12px;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      .btn{
        display:inline-flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:center;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
        transition: transform .14s ease, background .14s ease;
      }

      .btn:hover{ transform: translateY(-1px); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }
      .btn.primary{ border-color: rgba(9,255,3,0.22); background: rgba(9,255,3,0.10); }
      .btn.ghost{ background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }

      .card{
        margin: 18px 0;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      }

      .stack{ display:grid; gap: 12px; margin-top: 12px; }

      .ruleBlock{
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      }

      .ruleBlock p{ margin:0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); line-height: 1.6; }

      ul{
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      li{ margin: 6px 0; }
      strong{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92); }

      .footer{
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
        background: rgba(7,10,15,0.35);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .foot{
        display:flex;
        justify-content:space-between;
        gap:12px;
        padding: 16px 18px;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
      }

      .muted{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }

      @media (max-width: 820px){
        .links{ display:none; }
        .mobileJoin{ display:inline-flex; }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
